  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Comparing injectable collagenase and percutaneous needle fasciotomy for Dupuytren's
      contracture affecting proximal interphalangeal joints. An open label, medico-independent
      randomized controlled trial.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
